        <div class="content-section mb-5">
          <h3 class="h4 text-primary fw-bold">2. Purpose of Processing</h3>
          <p>At RumboMed, we process the information provided by interested parties for the following purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
            <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent border-0 ps-0"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-primary me-2"></i> To manage booking requests for vessels and nautical experiences.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent border-0 ps-0"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-primary me-2"></i> To respond to inquiries received through our contact channels.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent border-0 ps-0"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle text-primary me-2"></i> To send commercial communications about our offers and services (only with your prior consent).</li>
          </ul>
