          <p>Any person has the right to obtain confirmation as to whether RumboMed is processing personal data concerning them. You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled ps-3 mb-4">
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Access:</strong> Access your personal data.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Rectification:</strong> Request the rectification of inaccurate data.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request its deletion when the data is no longer necessary.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to the processing of your data.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert alert-info d-flex align-items-center rounded-3 border-0 shadow-sm" role="alert">
            <i class="bi bi-shield-check fs-3 me-3"></i>
            <div>
              To exercise these rights, you may send an email to <strong>info@rumbomed.com</strong> attaching a copy of your ID or equivalent document.
